---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
	title="Privacy Policy - Nature Near Me"
	description="Privacy policy for Nature Near Me - Learn how we collect, use, and protect your data when using our nature discovery platform."
	currentPage="privacy"
>
	<div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 max-w-4xl">
		<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
		
		<div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
			<p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}</p>
			
			<section class="mb-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
				<p class="mb-4">Nature Near Me collects minimal personal information to provide you with the best possible experience:</p>
				<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
					<li><strong>Location Data:</strong> Your approximate location (city/region level) to show relevant nature data near you</li>
					<li><strong>Usage Analytics:</strong> Anonymous usage statistics to improve our service</li>
					<li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Basic browser and device information for compatibility</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
				<p class="mb-4">We use the collected information to:</p>
				<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
					<li>Display relevant earthquakes, wildlife sightings, and natural features near your location</li>
					<li>Improve our website functionality and user experience</li>
					<li>Analyze usage patterns to enhance our services</li>
					<li>Ensure technical compatibility across different devices and browsers</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">3. Data Sharing and Third Parties</h2>
				<p class="mb-4">We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information. We may share data with:</p>
				<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
					<li><strong>Data Providers:</strong> USGS, eBird, and other nature data sources to fetch relevant information</li>
					<li><strong>Analytics Services:</strong> Anonymous usage data with Umami Analytics for website improvement</li>
					<li><strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> When required by law or to protect our rights and safety</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">4. Data Security</h2>
				<p class="mb-4">We implement appropriate security measures to protect your information:</p>
				<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
					<li>HTTPS encryption for all data transmission</li>
					<li>Regular security updates and monitoring</li>
					<li>Limited data retention periods</li>
					<li>No storage of sensitive personal information</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">5. Your Rights</h2>
				<p class="mb-4">You have the right to:</p>
				<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
					<li>Access any personal data we may have about you</li>
					<li>Request deletion of your data</li>
					<li>Opt out of analytics tracking</li>
					<li>Contact us with privacy concerns</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">6. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
				<p class="mb-4">We use minimal cookies and tracking:</p>
				<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
					<li><strong>Essential Cookies:</strong> For basic website functionality</li>
					<li><strong>Analytics:</strong> Anonymous usage tracking via Umami Analytics</li>
					<li><strong>No Advertising:</strong> We do not use advertising cookies or tracking</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">7. Children's Privacy</h2>
				<p class="mb-4">Nature Near Me is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you believe we have collected such information, please contact us immediately.</p>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
				<p class="mb-4">We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify users of any material changes by posting the new policy on this page and updating the "Last updated" date.</p>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">9. Contact Us</h2>
				<p class="mb-4">If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us:</p>
				<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
					<li>Email: privacy@naturenear.me</li>
					<li>Website: <a href="/contact" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">Contact Form</a></li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200">
				<a href="/" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">‚Üê Back to Nature Near Me</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout> 